{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","title":"handleOpenURL:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSURL","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"url"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The URL to process."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"url"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Test device registration","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Register device for push testing via QR code","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep link tracking"}]},{"text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"handleOpenURL:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"type":"topic"}}}